    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You accelerate the flow of Chakra in your body, enhancing your capabilities for a time. Your Base Attack Bonus increases to 3/4 th your level (as a Fast Hero), and your class bonus to Defense becomes equal to half your level (rounded down, minimum +1). These bonuses do not increase beyond 20 th level. In addition, you gain 1 temporary HP per level while the technique lasts.<br><br>The technique's cost is equal to: 5 + the Base Attack Bonus gained by this technique (i.e. if you go from +5 to +7, this technique costs 7 Chakra).<br><br>When the technique ends, you become @Condition[fatigued]{fatigued}. If you were already fatigued, you become @Condition[exhausted]{exhausted} instead.</p>\n\n\n\n",
